  рҹ”Қ Welcome, Nissim! The hunt begins!

  Session document initialized. I've loaded the project context вҖ” so I know we're operating in the BATbern world: software & product
  development, user problems, feature ideas, technical approaches, UX, business value, market differentiation, and more.

  Now let's set this session up for maximum creative momentum.

  ---
  Session Discovery Questions:

  1. What are we brainstorming about?
  (The central topic or challenge вҖ” could be a new feature, a product idea, a technical problem, a UX improvement, anything)
