  BATbern)
  2. batbern_history[] вҖ” the 57 (now 58) past event topics, each with its event number (already in BATbern вң…)
  3. topic_backlog[] вҖ” your internal list of candidate topics (needs to exist somewhere)
  4. ai_trending_topics[] вҖ” fetched fresh per session via AI/web search (new, lightweight)

  The good news: signals 1 and 2 already live in BATbern. The platform has partner interest data and event history. This tool is
  essentially a new visualization layer over data you already have. That's a much smaller build than it might seem.

