  Similarity engine: AI categorization against BATbern's own 58-topic taxonomy clusters вҖ” trustworthy, domain-specific, not
  general-purpose.

  Override mechanic: Drag any blob manually to merge or force proximity. Red blob held close = acknowledged warning. Stays as orbiting
  satellite.

  Decision: Double-click accepted blue blob вҶ’ session note auto-generated (topic, partner alignment, last covered N events ago, competing
   candidates).

  Canvas: Infinite, zoomable. Dark navy void. "Fit all" zoom-out button.

  Session mode: Single driver, shared screen, Teams call.

  Data sources: All already in BATbern except organizer backlog list (small addition to partner coordination page) + one AI
  trending-topics call at session start.

